data.description: Unobstructed views of Soldier Mountain and the Western Prairie. Large private corner lot give you the feel of living in the country. Renovated Manufactured home is move in ready. 2004 Fleetwood with New interior and exterior Paint, New Flooring, Full 3 bed  2 bath with single level master bed/bath. Open kitchen and 1400 sq. feet of living space provides comfortable living and low Maintenace expenses. Propane furnace and nearly new pellet stove. Propane tank is 500 gallon rented. Located in Fairfield Idaho, gateway to Soldier Mnt ski resort, hunting, fishing, snowmobiling and tons of outdoor recreation. 1.5 hrs from Boise, 1 hr from Sun Valley, 1 hr from Gooding.
